    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is primarily recommended for use as a parts donor or a major restoration project. The engine suffers from significant oil leaks and requires substantial mechanical work to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits frequent slipping. Additionally, the body has noticeable rust and several dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This is a non-running vehicle in its current state, offered as-is for someone with the tools and time to rebuild it.",
